`JavacAST ast = new JavacAST(messager, context, unit, cleanup);` every round will create ast for the same unit, if cache ast, it could compile faster.

LombokProcessor.process
```
		while (true) {
			// Step 2: For all CUs (in the map, not the roundEnv!), run them across all handlers at their current prio level.
			
			for (long prio : priorityLevels) {
